{"tid":849271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[泛民最無恥]梁家傑抹黑馮檢基無得退選柒左改post後唔順氣再踩多腳！","createTime":"2018-10-05T14:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T14:54:29.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3720fd9eb24fb6900086cb2df9b9705bebdd2dc","tid":849271,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/221432_8b4f637704e7e1332567c209293c1175.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F221432_8b4f637704e7e1332567c209293c1175.png&h=e834815e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先話馮檢基參選後無得退選，以此暗示馮檢基同共產黨有路一早知小麗會被DQ才參選。但梁家傑之後發現自己柒左，原來報名期內可以退選，於是鬼鬼鼠鼠改post變成&lsquo;報咗名又話會退選，是否多此一舉？&rsquo; 兜完後再踩多腳，盡顯梁家傑無恥人格！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民：明明自己柒左兜完都仲係要抽人水，點解你墮落到咁呢梁家傑？你需唔需要咁樣樣先？呢個唔係一個敵我鬥爭黎架ma! 大律師嚟㗎嘛你，做乜搞到成個八婆咁？鬧人俾啲理據啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Z-lvbdTgRQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Z-lvbdTgRQ&d=LVeiHdKwMKcZ54QT6wQ44XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9039d8e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Z-lvbdTgRQ</a><br />\n14:17"},{"pid":"7730eaa4a4d7134a485f5eee65ab2f980a6a069e","tid":849271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"為免五毛騎劫討論，大家請留意。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>習近平做鴨做殘廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"da6f97545e1c898982cf1d69d68b8f10e2c5b4d8","tid":849271,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}